@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using InfoSystem.Data.Entities
@inject SignInManager<User> SignInManager
@inject UserManager<User> UserManager

    <ul class="navbar-nav">
        @if (SignInManager.IsSignedIn(User))
        {
            <li class="nav-item">
                <form method="post" asp-action="logout" asp-controller="user">
                    <button type="submit" class="nav-link btn btn-link text-dark">Odhlásit @User.Identity.Name</button>
                </form>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link btn btn-link text-dark" asp-action="ChangePassword" asp-controller="user">
                    Změna hesla
                </a>
            </li>
        }
        else
        {
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-action="Create" asp-controller="UserAccessRequest">Zažádat o přístup</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-action="login" asp-controller="user">Přihlásit se</a>
            </li>
        }
    </ul>
